data.description: Looking for country living, here it is. Home built in 1914 full of charm and character. True craftsmanship with a new metal roof, large front porch with swing. Property has 3 acres, 1296 sq ft, 2 bd and 1 ba. Original pine wood floors through out. Front room floor has just been re-finished.  Kitchen and bath have ceramic tile flooring. Beautiful enclosed sun room.
